metadata.name: mySelf
metadata.description:
Drawn eyes-closed, one hand on mySelf and the other echoing it's movement with brush in hand, ink on paper.

Hannah Rose is interested in understanding and exploring the on-going importance of the female self portrait by artists today. She does this in her unique meditative style.

NFT is a digital image only of the original work being Chinese ink on paper. 
Copyrights remain with the artist
